org.talares.datatypes.items

Class Binary

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.talares.datatypes.items.Item
      • org.talares.datatypes.items.Binary

  • public class Binary
extends Item
    A Java representation of a Binary content type. Example Json: 
      {
    "__metadata": {
      "uri": "http://127.0.0.1:8080/cd_webservice/odata.svc/Binaries(BinaryId=123,PublicationId=1)",
      "type": "Tridion.ContentDelivery.Binary"
    },
    "BinaryId": 123,
    "PublicationId": 1,
    "Type": "application/vnd.ms-fontobject",
    "BinaryVariants": {
      "__deferred": {
        "uri": "http://127.0.0.1:8080/cd_webservice/odata.svc/Binaries(BinaryId=123,PublicationId=1)/BinaryVariants"
      }
    }
  }
    Since:
    0.1.0
